     C* B3: match-field comparison is sign-blind (manual 52317-52319):
     C* -5 (packed) in SBPRIM must match +5 (packed) in SBSEC -> MR on.
     C* RPGRET = 1 if MR fired, else 0.
     FSBPRIM  IP  F    1               DISK
     FSBSEC   IS  F    1               DISK
     ISBPRIM       1
     I                                    P   1   10PKEY    M1
     ISBSEC        2
     I                                    P   1   10SKEY    M1
     C           MR        Z-ADD1         RPGRET
